        "body":  "# Concentric vs Offset 0.5 mm Applanation Comparison\r\n\r\nThe offset case is 16a, confirmed from Body4 center X=0.5 mm.\r\nThe concentric case is 07_concentric_contact_all_rerun, confirmed from Body4 center X=0.0 mm.\r\n\r\nOffset 0.5 mm measured area ratio in the 0.20-0.32 mm window: 1.436 +/- 0.007.\r\nConcentric 0.0 mm rerun stores contact output, but the Body2-Body3 inner interface CONT,PRES field is zero in all five frames.\r\nTherefore a pressure-equivalent inner area coefficient is not reported for this older concentric MVP model.\r\n\r\nPlot: `concentric_vs_offset0p5_applanation.png`\r\n"
