        "meta":  "local simulation record / run catalog",
        "slug":  "blueknow-runs",
        "url":  "docs/blueknow-offset/runs_readme.md",
        "body":  "# Runs Catalog\r\n\r\n成功和可继续推进的实验已索引到 runs/_catalog/successful_experiments，每个实验一个文件夹。\r\n\r\nCurrent Workbench result target:\r\n- yeyeye_files/dp0/SYS/MECH/file.rst\r\n- Current intended result: MVP 0.6 mm compression, stabilized material, 0.1 s, PCG.\r\n\r\nLarge mesh follow-up script:\r\n- runs/fine_mvp_0p6mm_pcg_0p2s/run_fine_mvp_0p6mm_pcg_0p2s.ps1\r\n- Monitor with runs/fine_mvp_0p6mm_pcg_0p2s/monitor_fine_mvp_0p6mm_pcg_0p2s.ps1\r\n\r\nImportant: do not click Solve/Update in Mechanical when you only want to view copied/imported results; use Read Result Files and Evaluate All Results.\r\n\r\nLatest watched small-mesh experiment:\r\n- runs/smallmesh_mvp_0p6mm_0p1s_fine_substeps_watch\r\n- Catalog: runs/_catalog/successful_experiments/07_smallmesh_mvp_0p6mm_0p1s_fine_substeps\r\n\r\nFine mesh experiments:\r\n- 08 baseline: runs/fine_mvp_0p6mm_pcg_0p2s\r\n- 09 offset 1.0 mm: runs/fine_mvp_0p6mm_offset1p0mm_pcg_0p2s\r\n"
